    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-03-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-03-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="192"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d192">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 841.857/401</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Cork</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_FW1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Frost</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Cork</hi> (<hi rend="smallcaps"
                            >Queenstown</hi>)</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1917-03-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 13, 1917</hi>
                        </date>. <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 11 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Seven lives lost in sinking of Cunarder <hi rend="italic">Folia</hi> out of crew
                    of 78. <hi rend="italic">Folia</hi> bound New York to Avonmouth. Torpedoed
                    without warning 5 miles off Earn Head, County Water ford, in heavy fog Sunday,
                    7.20 a.m. Dr. <persName>Core</persName> and officers reach Bristol this morning.
                    Am telegraphing Consul there; this also to Ambassador, Consul General-</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_FW1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Frost</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
